name: Knowledge Unit 2 (KU2) Digital Applications Knowledge (option 1)
intro:
Digital Application Technician, Knowledge Unit 2 (KU2) 

This exam is a multiple-choice test and consists of 20 knowledge-based multiple-choice questions for you to answer. 

Each exam question will:

  • Have four options to choose from.
  • Only one option that is correct.
  • Each correct question will score 1 mark
  • Any missing or incorrect answers will score 0 marks

You will have 30 minutes to complete the exam and you will need a score of 13/20 (65%) or above to pass.
